category: Audio
requires: libglib2.0_0 libintl8 libncurses8 mpd
sdesc: "Curses client for the Music Player Daemon"
ldesc: "ncmpc is a curses client for the Music Player Daemon (MPD). 
ncmpc connects to a MPD running on a machine on the local network, and 
controls this with an interface inspired by cplay."
